song.title: No Time!
song.info: MAS_UTrack_V003 No Time! By: Killer Fish (Todd Showalter) of Late Nite Software Labs -------------------------------- Written on or about Mar/94. (c) This song was written as a response to about 12 deadlines, all of which descended on me from out of the clear blue sky. I spent a week of frantic work to get everything done, and when I had nothing left that needed to be done, this song is how I burned off the rest of my vast supply of adrenalin before I crawled into bed and fell into a deep, healing sleep. As usual, I have managed to use a 32 voice tracker to create a song that uses less than 10 channels. I'm working on wider music files (trust me...) but they won't be released until I can listen to them without openly cringing. May take a while... Greetz go to: C.C.Catch Ryan Cramer Purple Motion Deathjester Captain/Image Lizardking You guys make great music! Gotta speed, keid... Killer Fish
